21:09.875 --> 21:12.041
Everybody has their off days.

21:12.041 --> 21:15.083
I guess I just wanted
a little company.

21:15.083 --> 21:17.750
Besides, we have therapy later.
We can hit whatever--

21:17.750 --> 21:19.792
Sure.
Okay.

21:19.792 --> 21:21.375
Why waste it all
in rehearsal?

21:24.291 --> 21:27.250
And this is your terrace.

21:27.250 --> 21:30.417
It's got
2,000 square feet,

21:30.417 --> 21:33.166
Three hunded and sixty-degree
views, and as you can see,

21:33.166 --> 21:35.834
