21:35.834 --> 21:37.333
Wow.

21:37.333 --> 21:38.291
-Pretty f'ing sweet.
-Have a look.

21:38.291 --> 21:41.291
I'm gonna take this real quick.

21:43.542 --> 21:46.458
This is ridiculous.
You live here?

21:46.458 --> 21:49.125
Twelve floors down
and two lines over, but...

21:49.125 --> 21:51.000
Why don't you take
this place?

21:51.000 --> 21:52.834
Too much light.

21:52.834 --> 21:54.959
Anyway,
it's a bargain at $26,000.

21:54.959 --> 21:57.291
Twenty-six thousand
a month?

21:57.291 --> 21:58.291
Place I live now
costs twelve hundred.

21:58.291 --> 22:01.250
Taylor,
you're the golden child.

22:01.250 --> 22:04.000
End of the year,
Axe is gonna bonus you

22:04.000 --> 22:05.875
one point five minimum.

22:05.875 --> 22:07.542
Really?

22:08.208 --> 22:10.708
Hey, can you do me a favor?

22:10.708 --> 22:12.625
Axe is looking to make
a short play on Klaxon Auto.

22:12.625 --> 22:16.625
Assigned the write-up to me,
which I kicked to Ben Kim.

22:16.625 --> 22:19.500
Problem is, Ben doesn't see it
as a short.

22:19.500 --> 22:21.125
The numbers don't support it.

22:21.125 --> 22:23.375
I looked at it.
I don't think it is, either.

22:23.375 --> 22:25.583
- So tell Axe that.
- Yeah.

22:25.583 --> 22:28.208
I'd love to make the hero call,
stop Axe from losing money.

22:28.208 --> 22:31.834
Last time I tried,
he fired me.

22:31.834 --> 22:33.667
So you want me to review it.

22:33.667 --> 22:35.083
Would you?

22:35.083 --> 22:37.333
I'm not saying I've got
fucking dyscalculia,

22:37.333 --> 22:39.667
but if I'm gonna put my ass
on the chopping block,

22:39.667 --> 22:42.000
I want to make sure
I'm not missing something.

22:43.375 --> 22:45.542
Send the report over.
I'll take a look at it.

22:45.542 --> 22:46.875
Thanks.

22:46.875 --> 22:49.542
So?
Anybody out here need a pen?

22:49.542 --> 22:50.667
Can I get back to you?

22:50.667 --> 22:54.708
It's hitting MLS tomorrow.
It'll be gone by lunch.

22:54.708 --> 22:57.458
I'll get back to you
tonight.

23:04.083 --> 23:06.959
Thanks dude.

23:12.208 --> 23:14.000
Yeah.

23:14.000 --> 23:15.375
I have them at a go-kart track,

23:15.375 --> 23:17.625
a place called Autobahn,
for 90 minutes.

23:17.625 --> 23:19.417
Leaving
less than an hour ago.

23:19.417 --> 23:21.875
Anywhere near here
they might've headed?

23:21.875 --> 23:23.500
Yeah.
Yeah, there was a spot there

23:23.500 --> 23:25.166
she used to go
when she was young.

23:25.166 --> 23:26.750
She'd feel fortified there.

23:26.750 --> 23:29.583
-You want me to--
-No, no.

23:29.583 --> 23:31.417
I'll go.

23:33.917 --> 23:35.083
Gents.

23:37.625 --> 23:40.959
Hey, Axe.
Lara said you'd be showing up.

23:40.959 --> 23:42.750
You or someone
who worked for you.

23:42.750 --> 23:44.250
So she came in here?

23:44.250 --> 23:46.250
Yep, her and the boys.

23:46.250 --> 23:48.917
They fucking fleeced us
out of 20 bucks at darts.

23:48.917 --> 23:51.083
Soon as we tried to up the bet,
they quit.

23:51.083 --> 23:52.250
My boys.
They saw the hustle coming.

23:52.250 --> 23:53.542
Sure did.

23:53.542 --> 23:58.166
Anyway, uh, Lara said
to give her space.

23:58.166 --> 24:00.667
She was going
to your place in the city,

24:00.667 --> 24:03.125
and you could know that,
but to please respect.

24:03.125 --> 24:04.917
She'll get in touch
when she's ready.

24:04.917 --> 24:07.208
And so I'm supposed to what?
Just fucking sit

24:07.208 --> 24:09.500
-on my goddamn--
-You can press her.

24:09.500 --> 24:12.458
But look,
you know her better than us.

24:12.458 --> 24:13.500
You do that and--

24:13.500 --> 24:16.792
Yep. I'll make this look
like the Rose Parade.

24:19.875 --> 24:23.083
Hey, it's me.
I went to Terry's bar.

24:23.083 --> 24:25.917
The memories came flooding back.

24:25.917 --> 24:28.000
Us there at the beginning,

24:28.000 --> 24:29.250
right after I got struck
by the thunderbolt

24:29.250 --> 24:33.166
like Michael with Apollonia.

24:33.166 --> 24:35.750
And I was thinking about

24:35.750 --> 24:39.083
all that rail shit
we used to drink,

24:39.083 --> 24:43.458
but we were already drunk
from being with each other,

24:43.458 --> 24:45.083
so we didn't care.

24:45.083 --> 24:48.458
And then I flipped totally
to the other extreme.

24:49.583 --> 24:52.750
To Paris. That rainy night.

24:52.750 --> 24:55.875
We wouldn't get out of bed
even though the iPod

24:55.875 --> 24:58.083
was playing
"With or Without You" on repeat,

24:58.083 --> 25:00.875
and so we ended up
listening to it all night.

25:00.875 --> 25:03.792
And I was just thinking...

25:03.792 --> 25:08.667
I was thinking how deep it got
between us.

25:08.667 --> 25:11.542
And we promised that if anything
ever threatened us,

25:11.542 --> 25:14.500
we'd remind ourselves
of that night

25:14.500 --> 25:16.834
and we'd try to find
a way back to it.

25:16.834 --> 25:21.583
And I'm reminding you
of that night right now.

25:21.583 --> 25:26.041
Let's fight our way back to it.

25:26.041 --> 25:28.875
Call me, please.

25:34.625 --> 25:38.083
Thank you for finding the time,
Mr. Martinez.

25:38.083 --> 25:39.375
What's the urgent matter?

25:39.375 --> 25:42.375
My laptop was stolen
by a client.

25:44.291 --> 25:45.959
Can you tell me who?

25:45.959 --> 25:47.458
Gave me a backstopped alias.

25:47.458 --> 25:50.708
Came to me for three months.

25:50.708 --> 25:53.041
Worked his way
into my inner sanctum.

25:53.041 --> 25:54.708
You think it's an attack
against me?

25:54.708 --> 25:57.166
You or one of my more
prominent clients.

25:57.166 --> 25:59.417
More prominent than I?

25:59.417 --> 26:01.417
Should come
as no surprise to you

26:01.417 --> 26:03.291
the lifestyle attracts
brilliant people.

26:03.291 --> 26:04.250
Mm-hmm.

26:04.250 --> 26:06.208
Intricate temperaments.

26:06.208 --> 26:09.083
Intricate tastes.

26:09.083 --> 26:11.792
How protected
is your information?

26:11.792 --> 26:15.125
I have a deeply devoted client
from Palo Alto

26:15.125 --> 26:17.375
who's in corporate
cyber defense.

26:17.375 --> 26:19.834
You may rest assured.

26:19.834 --> 26:22.166
And if I were ever approached
personally--

26:22.166 --> 26:25.708
I know that your relationships
are beyond transactional.

26:25.708 --> 26:26.708
The idea
of blackmailing someone

26:26.708 --> 26:28.750
with something so close
to their core,

26:28.750 --> 26:32.750
-of punishing true expression--
-Understood.

26:32.750 --> 26:35.250
Understood.

26:35.250 --> 26:36.875
And thank you.

26:45.375 --> 26:47.583
Pick that up.

27:01.834 --> 27:03.000
It's good to see you again,
Mr. Martinez.

27:03.000 --> 27:05.125
Hmm.

27:05.125 --> 27:06.834
We should do it again
under other circumstances.

27:09.000 --> 27:12.250
Once you've secured
proper permissions, of course.

27:12.250 --> 27:14.542
Of course.

27:33.834 --> 27:35.708
Did you find her?

27:36.166 --> 27:38.500
Yes.

27:39.667 --> 27:42.750
She went into the city
with the boys, but I don't...

27:42.750 --> 27:44.208
know how to bring them home.

27:44.208 --> 27:45.417
I'm sorry.

27:45.417 --> 27:46.959
What do you want?

27:46.959 --> 27:49.750
What I've always wanted,
to help.

27:53.834 --> 27:58.959
I was remembering...
when you first met her.

27:58.959 --> 28:01.000
Me, too.

28:01.000 --> 28:02.834
And you said you felt like
you'd known her forever.

28:02.834 --> 28:05.959
Everyone else was sucking up,
angling.

28:05.959 --> 28:10.041
One date and you were talking
about marriage.

28:11.000 --> 28:11.667
I was skeptical.

28:11.667 --> 28:14.083
I thought that sort of thing

28:14.083 --> 28:17.333
only happened
in the Sicilian hills.

28:17.333 --> 28:20.542
And then I met her.

28:20.542 --> 28:22.583
Then it all made sense.

28:23.708 --> 28:26.834
You know,
she had three close friends

28:26.834 --> 28:28.250
who lost their husbands
on 9/11.

28:28.250 --> 28:30.166
Firemen.

28:30.166 --> 28:33.083
And she helped
to prop them all up,

28:33.083 --> 28:35.208
even after losing
her own brother.

28:35.208 --> 28:37.125
She helped them clean out
their closets,

28:37.125 --> 28:39.875
and you wouldn't think that
that was the toughest thing,

28:39.875 --> 28:42.708
but the way they wept
when they found

28:42.708 --> 28:45.542
a favorite t-shirt
or an old varsity jacket

28:45.542 --> 28:47.875
or a wedding suit.

28:47.875 --> 28:50.708
And then about a week later,
something occurred to her,

28:50.708 --> 28:53.625
and for all three of them,

28:53.625 --> 28:57.708
she found a way to get back
into their bedrooms.

28:57.708 --> 29:01.041
And she crawled under the beds

29:01.041 --> 29:05.458
and retrieved the errant
slipper or sneaker.

29:07.333 --> 29:10.708
She defended them from
those little land mines.

29:10.708 --> 29:13.708
You don't talk
about that side of her much.

29:17.166 --> 29:22.166
Look, I, um...
I know that you feel bad.

29:23.750 --> 29:26.875
But that doesn't fix anything
'cause I tried.

29:28.708 --> 29:30.834
I'm limited to waiting now,

29:30.834 --> 29:33.250
and you know
the problem with that?

29:33.250 --> 29:35.500
You fucking hate waiting.

29:37.542 --> 29:40.667
♪ pensive music  ♪

29:57.708 --> 30:00.458
Hi, it's Lara.
Leave a message.

30:00.458 --> 30:03.375
Hey, it's me again.

30:03.375 --> 30:05.667
You know what?
Maybe I was wrong.

30:05.667 --> 30:08.000
Maybe Wendy Rhoades
isn't helping.

30:08.000 --> 30:11.834
Maybe I should just blow her
the fuck out of our lives.

30:11.834 --> 30:16.750
Whatever it takes to get
you home, get us talking again,

30:16.750 --> 30:19.375
just say the word,

30:19.375 --> 30:22.959
and I'll erase Wendy Rhoades
from our world forever.

30:26.792 --> 30:32.458
Oh.
Quick second date.

30:32.458 --> 30:34.959
On the hazing,

30:34.959 --> 30:37.959
the whole
Code Red situation,

30:37.959 --> 30:41.917
you were the victim,
not one of the aggressors.

30:41.917 --> 30:44.834
You were Santiago,
not Dawson.

30:47.542 --> 30:50.542
Boy, they left me black and blue
anywhere my shirt would hide.

30:50.542 --> 30:52.125
And you told on them?

30:52.125 --> 30:53.583
Oh, no.

30:53.583 --> 30:55.125
Oh, it had
its desired effect.

30:55.125 --> 30:57.500
I never breathed a word.

30:57.500 --> 30:59.834
Until just now.

30:59.834 --> 31:02.875
But later,

31:02.875 --> 31:07.166
not a few days,
two years later...

31:07.166 --> 31:08.959
intramural baseball.

31:08.959 --> 31:12.834
I was at bat,
the ringleader was catching.

31:12.834 --> 31:16.667
And on one fast ball,
I swung backwards.

31:16.667 --> 31:19.500
Lefty.

31:19.500 --> 31:21.542
Right into his face.

31:21.542 --> 31:23.000
Was he wearing a mask?

31:23.000 --> 31:24.750
Yeah,
that's why his head stayed on,

31:24.750 --> 31:28.083
but his jaw... shattered.

31:31.708 --> 31:33.750
Now, is that gonna come back
and bite me?

31:33.750 --> 31:36.834
If you hadn't told me,
could've ended your campaign,

31:36.834 --> 31:38.917
but I know how to spin it

31:38.917 --> 31:41.041
as a strong
anti-bullying stance.

31:41.041 --> 31:42.375
By the time I'm finished
with you,

31:42.375 --> 31:46.875
you'll be signing baseball bats
every time you appear in public.

31:46.875 --> 31:49.166
Okay.

31:52.875 --> 31:57.041
My biggest potential
vulnerability.

32:00.291 --> 32:02.375
Now it's in your hands.

32:02.375 --> 32:03.333
Any chance
the, uh, operative

32:03.333 --> 32:05.750
could've copied
the hard drive on this?

32:05.750 --> 32:09.750
No.
He's a trusted.

32:09.750 --> 32:13.625
♪ dramatic music  ♪

32:21.750 --> 32:24.500
I'll have my tech people run
a lice comb through this.

32:24.500 --> 32:25.583
Mm.
You'll let me know.

32:25.583 --> 32:27.500
-And the owner of this?
-Also a trusted.

32:27.500 --> 32:29.125
Hundred percent?

32:29.125 --> 32:30.792
No such thing.

32:30.792 --> 32:34.959
Now you're getting it.
Good.

32:34.959 --> 32:36.583
Good.

32:48.625 --> 32:53.625
